name: Bib - Horses Grey
description:
This bib is made from 100% cotton fabric and backed with soft bamboo terry.

Bamboo is highly water absorbent, approximately 60% more water absorbent than cotton.

It features two industrial strength resin snaps setting for adjustability at the neck.

Size: 
Approximately 22cm (8.7") wide x 34cm (13.5") high

Care:
Machine wash in cold water.
